== Entering Fastboot mode ==

Power off the device. Hold <code>Back</code> as you plug the USB cable into the device.

== Bootloader unlocking ==
The process of unlocking the bootloader officially is available '''[https://developer.sony.com/develop/open-devices/get-started/unlock-bootloader/ here]''' and it is strictly adviced to use it in the first place. It has all the instructions for one to unlock it.

