== What works ==

* Building and installing to external SD card
* Display
* Touchscreen
* USB networking
* Xwayland

== What does not work ==

* Plasma Mobile
* Hardware accelerated graphics
* Audio
* Bluetooth
* GPS
* Camera
* Mobile data
* Phone calls

Note that Wi-Fi and osk-sdl are untested and may require further work.

